snippet.title: Diablo IV | Season of the Malignant | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
A new threat is corrupting Sanctuary.

#DiabloIV Season of the Malignant is coming July 20th. Will you be ready?

Visit diablo.com to test your fate in #DiabloIV and prepare for the evil to come.
